official_title: Sonography of the Nipple Areolar Complex (SONAC) Study
inclusion_criteria:
Female, Age of 18 or older; no breast cancer; no breast symptom.
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
exclusion_criteria:
Subjects lacking capacity to consent; vulnerable subjects such as prisoners.

Note: Other protocol defined Inclusion/Exclusion Criteria may apply.
